{"tid":417171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府一日重有辣招，樓價一日都唔會跌","createTime":"2017-09-28T12:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T12:35:32.000Z","uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3aef1b22b23623fd16c726e250e567ee26ac7861","tid":417171,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T12:00:56.000Z","msg":"二手辣招已經冰結哂二手供應<br />\n一手價錢由發展商主導 下下新高<br />\n<br />\n辣招未解，跟本顯示政府冇決心解決樓價問題<br />\n首置，貨櫃屋只是綽頭野卜"},{"pid":"443ac82e8346048c8171bf12645569ac191324e9","tid":417171,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T12:02:19.000Z","msg":"最清醒係你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62df8dfe98948f0deb513262b95373d5067d53d8","tid":417171,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T12:17:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最清醒係你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試把 樓宇供應想像成災難飢荒<br />\n災民急需食物，而政府把食物不但囤積居奇，仲連同其他大商家合謀控制供應，不停加價，咁都唔係趁火打劫？<br />\n而家就係囤貨既貨倉度拎少少去塞你班人把口<br />\n個根本原因根本冇解決。<br />\n而家根本就係要加大居屋私樓的供應"},{"pid":"145504ab039635d95cb2499f6444652a1abd35f6","tid":417171,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T12:19:57.000Z","msg":"我當辣招取消，樓價會爆升<br />\n升多2年必爆泡沫<br />\n<br />\n但而家咁樣<br />\n冇10年都唔爆"},{"pid":"21a88ef0032859cf49084f31ab18e79bbdfecf75","tid":417171,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T12:26:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"662ad4a56bca52aedb1cfa9ba3196724a2376209","tid":417171,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T12:35:32.000Z","msg":"等死好過啦<br />\n等佢跌喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}